<br>
We wanted pets to be immune to fear, and we got it.  It's a gimpy spell that doesn't last long enough, but we got it.<br>
<br>
We asked for pet SOW.  We got pet JBoot speed, but for some strange reason pet SOW is one of the rarest drops and there's more reasons to not cast it than to cast it.<br>
<br>
We asked for pets to not eat a wave of rains, which is really handy in PvP and made mages more welcome in AE groups.  I very rarely see AE groups so again, it's hardly an issue.<br>
<br>
