<br>
We got pet heals.  So... Quick trivia quiz.  Would you rather:<br>
A) Spend 400 mana to heal your pet for 900 hit points or<br>
B) Spend 400 mana to summon a new Greater Voceration pet for 2800 hit points?<br>
<br>
The heals are a red herring.  Distracting, but not that useful.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
