<br>
I made my mage after leveling a warrior to 58.  Frankly, warriors got spoiled.  My damage output jumped bigtime with Kunark and then again with Velious.  Skills like Defensive made me a solid #1 tank.  Those were some real, big time, heavy hitting, serious enhancements.<br>
<br>
